Changed Connect in Apex Output Classes

Commerce
ConnectApi.AbstractCartItem: customFields—Array of sObjects and viewable custom fields for the sObjects.
ConnectApi.CartItem: unitAdjustedPriceWithItemAdj—Unit price, including both tier and item level discounts, informational only. unitItemAdjustmentAmount—Item level adjustments made to the unit price for the item, informational only. 
ConnectApi.CartSummary: totalAmountWithItemAdjustment—Total amount, including both tier and item level discounts but excluding cart level discounts, informational only. totalCartLevelAdjustmentAmount—Total cart level discount amount used for the cart, informational only.

Einstein
ConnectApi.EinsteinLLMGenerationItemOutput: contentQualityRepresentation—Specifies whether the generated response contains toxic language (true) or not (false).

Orchestration
ConnectApi.OrchestrationWorkItem: createdDate—Date when the work item was created. lastModifiedDate—Date when the work item was last modified.

Salesforce CMS
ConnectApi.ManagedContentDocument: apiName—API name of the managed content.
ConnectApi.ManagedContentSpace: apiName—API name of the managed content space.
